The paper discusses a model for image reconstruction and pattern recognition, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of algorithms and harmonic analysis also suggests that it could belong to the numerical analysis (cs.NA) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the development of a theory, which could place it in the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category. Finally, the use of efficient algorithms suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
